<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>/pet hold</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, making it <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">ignore</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> its hate list, followed by:<br>
