<br>
seems like every mob in PoP enrages, so I am in the habit of slamming pet hold when the mob is at 15% life or so. This also ensures the pet doesn't do anything strange during pulls.<br>
<br>
The problem with doing pet back off with and only with the pet hold is that if the pet picks up ahte from something between the time you did pet hold and the time you do attack, it can go on the wrong target. <p>Master Cydmab Promethean<br>
