I can't really think of a time when I would want to call my pet off and not clear his hatelist.  Hence combining the hold and the back off.  Clearing the hate list mid battle to keep the pet focused or move him to a new mob is something I do conciously by using both hotkeys.  I don't always want to clear his hate list when sending him on a new target, I could just be building up a &quot;to kill&quot; list (like clearing trash in KD where nothing is mezzable anyway). <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=103898" target="top">Master Evelle Fyrestrike</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
